HDTV Katy Perry - VH1 Divas Salute the Troops, USA, 2010 [1080p59.94] - caladan

    I extracted the videos from a TV broadcast. I deinterlaced with QTGMC + deblocked the video + made even top and bottom black bars (it had just one tiny top black bar) + converted audio to stereo and amplified the volume. Also I fixed the aspect ratio of the B&W sequence of the first video (the frame was stretched, so the artists looked like they were elongated). I think it looks much better than the source.

    Content:
    01. Katy Perry, Keri Hilson & Jennifer Nettles - Boogie Woogie Bugle Boy
    02. Katy Perry - California Gurls
    03. Katy Perry & Nicki Minaj - Girls Just Want to Have Fun
    04. Katy Perry - Firework
